# Sensitive repos — operations against these must ONLY be performed
# under a bot/service account, NEVER your personal identity. A push,
# merge, PR, or release that lands under your personal account on one
# of these would attach your name to it permanently.
#
# Format: one egrep-style regex per line. # = comment.
# Match against the "owner/repo" portion of the remote URL.
#
# Examples (replace with your own):
your-org/your-private-repo
your-org/another-private-repo
